tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T9 at the 98th Abierto del Sur in Mar del Plata, Argentina [Argentina Tour/DevSeries event] on his first start as a professional.
tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Despite being the only amateur in a 60-player field battling for PGA TOUR Latinoamérica status at the Developmental Series Final in Ecuador, he prevailed with the authority of a veteran. Shot 67-66-66 to open an eight-shot lead and carded a 70 on the final round to win by four. His total of 269 (-15) set a new 72-hole record at Arrayanes Country Club. The victory secured him exempt status for the PGA TOUR Latinoamérica 2016 season.
tourBios.personal: Picked up the game at the age of 15… Twitter name is @matias_simaski
